description:
The Bug Shield zips to any Veer Retractable Canopy (sold separately) and stretches across the top of Cruiser to help keep bugs away from little ones. Use of the bug shield is suitable for one seated passenger. Note that the Bug Shield comes standard with the Nap System.

FEATURES


Includes Sun Shade/Bug Shield (attaches to Canopy, sold separately) and Storage Bag


Zips to a retractable canopy


Attaches to the opposite seatback


Easy to store in sidewall pockets



SPECIFICATIONS

Suitability: Parental Suitability
Product Dimensions: L: 600mm x W: 490mm x H: 400mm
Weight: 0.072 kg


SUPPORT MATERIAL
 Instruction Manual
